Articles.Content:
You can adjust the pressure at which they open, as they need a minimum, causing the chutes to open at lower altitudes than set sometimes.

Spoiler

@PART[\*]:HAS[@MODULE[SSTUModularParachute]]:NEEDS[SSTU]:AFTER[SSTU]  

{  

    @MODULE[SSTUModularParachute]  

    {  

        @stagingEnabled = true  

        @mainMaxQ = 60000  

    }  

}

I don't think you can change the max altitude beyond what the slider allow.
